headline: Nominations Now Open for Henry Schein Medical’s Athletics and Schools 2025 Rising Star Award
summary: MELVILLE, N.Y., February 26, 2025--In celebration of National Athletic Training Month in March, Henry Schein Medical, the U.S. medical business of Henry Schein, Inc. (Nasdaq: HSIC), is now accepting nominations for its Henry Schein Medical Athletics and Schools 2025 Rising Star Award.
